snippet.title: Hajis - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Hajis

Coming on 25th of October

Hajis is a survival horror co-op game 2-4 players.
You have to maintain your mentality in an place where talking, footsteps or any sounds you make can cause your death.
_
Website: https://www.vioegame.com/
Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1928670/Hajis/
